---
title: Orecchiette with Herbed Pork Tenderstem Broccoli, Chilli and Pesto (5 MEAL)
description: If you were spending a weekend in Rome then you might come across this dish under it’s traditional name, ‘Orecchiette ai Broccoletti’. It’s a classic Italian dish combining a few simple, yet incredibly high quality ingredients for a quick, nutritious, delicious dinner. A plateful of nutritious deliciousness in the time it takes to boil your pasta!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54be58d16ced6edc218b4567.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/54be58d16ced6edc218b4567.pdf
cuisine: Italian
nutrition:
  calories: 794 kcal
  fat: 36 g
  saturated fat: 11 g
  carbohydrates: 84 g
  protein: 33 g
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
